About Habitat Homes
Join One Of Our Affordable Communities Now!
Our Mission
Our mission is to operate and manage safe, clean and resident focused communities where pride of residency is expected. We take pride in our communities, and make sure that each individual, and family is taken care of and has pride of residency. We're not your typical company -- we work hard, and have a passion for what we do everyday because we believe that the residents and the families that call our communities home are the backbone of the communities themselves.
We come to work not for ourselves, but our community residents that have a need that we are fulfilling. We love our communities and are focused on continual improvements. We focus on filling our communities with residents that make our communities stronger. We build better communities through our work and our continued efforts to see our spaces become better for all residents that call it home.
The Foundation of Habitat Homes
Operating Communities that strive to be Safe, Clean and Community First. Operating with Integrity and Honesty.
Community First
We are relationship driven. Our community members are important to us – we look for connections with our residents.
Honesty
At Habitat Communities, we strive to fulfill all of our commitments to our residents and our employees.
Integrity​
All community residents are treated with respect and equality. We are all human and deserve respect.
Safety​
From cleanliness to physical hazard, we intend for our communities to be safe for residents of all ages and backgrounds.
Home buying can be a stressful process, but we take the guess work out of finding a the right manufactured home for you and your family. We’ll help you find the perfect match to purchase your ideal home.
